      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="ECS部署hexo博客系统总结"><a href="#ECS部署hexo博客系统总结" class="headerlink" title="ECS部署hexo博客系统总结"></a>ECS部署hexo博客系统总结</h2><p>一、申请阿里云ECS + 公网IP</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://free.aliyun.com" target="_blank" rel="external">半年免费套餐：</a></li>
</ul>
<p>二、<a href="https://wanwang.aliyun.com/domain/" target="_blank" rel="external">申请和购买域名</a></p>
<p>三、<a href="https://help.aliyun.com/knowledge_detail/39783.html" target="_blank" rel="external">设置域名解析</a></p>
