<p>五、<a href="https://ninghao.net/video/3550" target="_blank" rel="external">SSH连接服务器、建立非root用户、SSH免密码登陆</a></p>
<p>六、<a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/834d7cc0668d" target="_blank" rel="external">部署本地hexo博客系统，可以git发布到github.io</a></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://material.viosey.com/start/#install-material" target="_blank" rel="external">主题选择</a></li>
<li><p><a href="https://github.com/jaredly/hexo-admin" target="_blank" rel="external">管理界面</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://material.viosey.com/services/" target="_blank" rel="external">站内搜索</a></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">注意：对于本地搜索，主题的config设置：search  use: local</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ul>
<p>七、本地hexo博客，发布到ECS目录</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.jianshu.com/p/605c3d32cab9" target="_blank" rel="external">安装nginx，并使用 rsync 将 Hexo 部署到远程</a>    </li>
<li><a href="http://www.stephenzhang.me/2017/07/06/hexo-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91ECS-CentOS7-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/" target="_blank" rel="external">参考二</a></li>
</ul>
<p>八、<a href="https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/50775.html" target="_blank" rel="external">ECS部署nodes项目</a></p>
